{
  "stem": "8916.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, towards the end, the orders came down from headquarters that all these people in these camps were to be killed before the-- the-- they left, before the-- the army of liberations came.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In this-- in our case, it was the Russians.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in-- in other cases were the Allies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were-- he was actually preparing to do just that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But Schindler somehow talked him out of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He-- he-- he had a way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he had actually given him some papers to tell him that-- false papers-- that-- that he was needed in Berlin or something, and he-- he left.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The commandant left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so we were left with a small group of SS guards, and they were pretty much-- pretty well defeated by that time, you know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not very much.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At this-- by that point-- at that point, Schindler had more control over what was happening in the camp than-- than he did before.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Before, he-- the camps were really controlled by the SS.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in Brunnlitz we were about eight months, and then we-- the-- the Russians came in, and we were liberated there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were-- we were-- actually, the factory was reestablished, and we were doing work in the-- in the factory, working 12-hour shifts.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were, at that point, you know, with-- at the-- in Emalia, we were making pots and pans and war-related things.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then when we got to-- to Brunnlitz, it was just the war-related product that we were trying to reestablish.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it never got to the point where anything was shipped.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did you know that you weren't getting anywhere with your efforts, or that you-- Well, we were going along as if progress was being made.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
